text:
Li Weiwei (born 17 November 1994) is a Chinese female volleyball player. She was part of the China women's national volleyball team. She participated in the 2010 FIVB World League, 2013 FIVB Volleyball Women's U20 World Championship, and 2015 FIVB Volleyball Women's U23 World Championship.
She played for Beijing BAIC Motor women's volleyball team.
